{"type":null,"faqId":47318,"title":"如何设置通过 USB 共享网络？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.40347221in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.1930555in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">因为操作系统的差异，在使用此功能前，可能需要在电脑中安装手机驱动程序或建立相应的网络连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span class=\"s1\">使用 USB 数据线将手机与电脑连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span class=\"s1\">在主屏幕，点击“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“更多…”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 4  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“网络共享与便携式热点”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 5  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击 “USB网络共享”开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175723\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">通过 USB 共享移动网络时，手机将不能作为 USB 存储设备使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2885","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219214000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":79,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"USB,网络,共享","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}